From: Paul Jackson <pj@sgi.com>
Subject: Replace pairs of calls to <atomic_inc, atomic_read>, with a single call atomic_inc_return, saving a few bytes of source and kernel text.
References: 150185

Signed-off-by: Paul Jackson <pj@sgi.com>
Signed-off-by: Andrew Morton <akpm@osdl.org>
Acked-by: Andreas Gruenbacher <agruen@suse.de>
